  "texts": [
    "To prove this, we work iteratively with the lower central series 𝔫 i:= [𝔫, 𝔫 i-1], 𝔫 1 = 𝔫.",
    "We will construct, by induction on k, a U k such that U k + F (U k) ∈ 𝔫 k+1.",
    "For the base case, we look at (37) modulo 𝔫 2.",
    "Since D is a derivation, it preserves 𝔫 2, and it hence induces an invertible map on 𝔫 1 /𝔫 2.",
    "On the other hand, F (U) modulo 𝔫 2 is simply the image of Y in 𝔫 1 /𝔫 2, therefore we can always find U 1 solving (37) modulo 𝔫 2."
  ],
